headline: Service and Support: Regions Bank Launches Disaster-Recovery Options for Consumers, Businesses
summary: BIRMINGHAM, Ala., April 15, 2025--Regions Bank on Tuesday announced a series of disaster-recovery financial services designed to help people and businesses impacted by devastating severe storms, tornadoes and flooding that affected parts of the Midwest and Southeast from April 2 through April 7.
